Frank Losee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frank_Losee 0 Frank Losee (June 12, 1856 – November 14, 1937) was an American stage and screen actor. A veteran of the Broadway stage he began in silent films in 1915. Often he played the father of Mary Pickford, Pauline Frederick and Marguerite Clark.His wife was Marion Elmore.
